name: Lost in Supermarket
description:
This work is to celebrate my one month in the NFT community. Thank you for your support and generosity!

This photo was taken in my early days using photography as an artistic tool. Also, this photo is part of a photo-zine entitled "Avaritia"—published in 2018. Made using a cheap point & shoot camera, pushed Tri-X Film, and dissolved in homemade parodinal.
